# CLAUDE.md

## Project Overview

__COPILOT_NAME__ Voice Assistant — a React SPA with voice agent integration. Originally generated from **Figma Make**, with voice capabilities added via `@unctad-ai/voice-agent-*` packages.

## Commands

- `docker compose up -d` — start frontend + backend
- `docker compose down` — stop all services
- `docker compose logs -f` — tail logs
- `docker compose up --build -d` — rebuild after changes
- `npm install` — install dependencies (without Docker)
- `npm run dev` — start Vite dev server (without Docker)
- `npm run build` — production build to `build/`

## Docker Compose

Two services: `frontend` (Vite/nginx, port 80) + `backend` (Express, port 3001). Backend reads `server/.env` for API keys.

## Architecture

**Stack:** React + TypeScript + Vite + voice-agent-kit

**Voice Agent:**
- `src/voice-config.ts` — Client SiteConfig (copilot name, colors, services, routes)
- `server/voice-config.ts` — Server SiteConfig (adds server tools, system prompt)
- `server/index.ts` — Express server with chat/STT/TTS endpoints
- `src/App.tsx` — VoiceAgentProvider wrapping the app + GlassCopilotPanel

**Voice-agent-kit packages:**
- `@unctad-ai/voice-agent-core` — Hooks, types, config
- `@unctad-ai/voice-agent-ui` — UI components (GlassCopilotPanel, VoiceOrb)
- `@unctad-ai/voice-agent-registries` — Form fields, UI actions, tool handlers
- `@unctad-ai/voice-agent-server` — Express route handlers

## Environment Variables (server/.env)

```
GROQ_API_KEY=...           # Required: Groq API key for LLM + Whisper STT
STT_URL=...                # STT endpoint URL
QWEN3_TTS_URL=...          # TTS endpoint URL
CLIENT_API_KEY=...         # API key for frontend→backend auth
COPILOT_NAME=__COPILOT_NAME__
```
